Package: pdchecker
Title: Protocol Deviation Checker for Clinical Trials
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Qinghuan", "Wang", , "qinghuan.wang@qilu-pharma.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Automates the detection of protocol deviations in clinical
    trials. Provides tools to read SAS and Excel datasets, parse visit
    schedules with window periods, generate planned visit dates per
    subject, and perform checks on informed consent timing, visit
    compliance, and laboratory test completeness. Results can be exported
    as Markdown, HTML, or Excel reports.
